Then we will taste each other's ashes.

206
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:57,360
這是夢  只是個白日夢而已
This is a dream... nothing but a waking dream.

207
00:13:58,690 --> 00:13:59,570
那個面具
The mask.

208
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:03,070
