The fact that you offer them up so eagerly attests to that.

252
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:03,230
但你已經進步不少了
But you made great progress.

253
00:17:04,270 --> 00:17:07,750
我們就要撥開謊言的迷霧了
We are working our way through the lies.

254
00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:15,650
要不了多久  那一刻就會到來
Very soon, we will come to that precise moment

255
00:17:15,650 --> 00:17:19,460
當痛苦難以承受
when the agony will be so unendurable

256
00:17:19,460 --> 00:17:22,370
