but my mother and sisters are not.

300
00:21:32,040 --> 00:21:33,930
他們還強迫我去看
and they forced me to watch.

301
00:21:34,860 --> 00:21:37,540
之后  掛著鐐銬的我回頭望去
Later, in chains, I look back,

302
00:21:37,570 --> 00:21:40,510
他們將村里的棚屋付之一炬
and they're burning the huts of my village,

303
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:43,750
