Cotton, get your drunk ass down here.

319
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:44,630
不  我就不
No, sir, I will not.

320
00:22:44,890 --> 00:22:46,750
我在這兒站得高看得遠
I can see far more clearly from here.

321
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:48,270
不光看得遠  什么都看得見
In fact, I can see everything.

322
00:22:48,270 --> 00:22:50,780
