是薩勒姆恐怖事件的幕后黑手時有多驚訝
stands behind all of Salem's horror.

565
00:40:51,260 --> 00:40:55,010
我恐怕  需要呼吸點新鮮空氣
I fear I...need a breath of air.

566
00:40:55,240 --> 00:40:58,560
能和我出去走走嗎  瑪麗·西布里
Will you walk with me, Mary Sibley,

567
00:41:00,610 --> 00:41:01,870
在夜晚的清爽中
In the evening air...

568
00:41:04,490 --> 00:41:07,610
也許我們能找到一個好地方
where we may have a good vantage point

569
00:41:07,820 --> 00:41:09,960
觀看一場逮捕
from which to witness an arrest?

570
00:41:15,570 --> 00:41:18,260
我想回去看看柯頓怎么樣了
I'm tempted to go back, see if Cotton's all right.

571
00:41:18,830 --> 00:41:20,260
他可能會在森林里迷路
He could get lost in those woods

572
00:41:20,270 --> 00:41:22,520
然后在熊的肚子里醒來
and wake up inside the belly of a bear.

573
00:41:23,220 --> 00:41:24,270
他在那
There he is!

574
00:41:41,170 --> 00:41:42,100
約翰·奧登
John Alden...

575
00:41:46,800 --> 00:41:48,620
奉英克里斯·麥哲之命
...by order of Increase Mather

576
00:41:48,620 --> 00:41:50,850
以塞勒姆行政委員之名
and in the name of the selectmen of Salem,

577
00:41:51,660 --> 00:41:53,540
我宣布逮捕你
I place you under arrest.

578
00:42:03,210 --> 00:42:04,280
這次又是因為什么
What for this time?

579
00:42:06,030 --> 00:42:07,390
公開說臟話嗎
Swearing in public?

580
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:09,550
巫術
Witchcraft.

581
00:42:11,850 --> 00:42:13,990
解除他的武裝  拷上他
Disarm him, shackle him.

582
00:42:15,310 --> 00:42:16,090
不
No!

583
00:42:16,510 --> 00:42:18,750
不  父親  阻止他們
No! Father, stop them!

584
00:42:19,440 --> 00:42:20,680
父親  求你了
Father, please!

585
00:42:20,720 --> 00:42:22,420
求你了  你有能力  你可以做些什么
Please! You have the power to do something!

586
00:42:22,420 --> 00:42:23,750
等著
Wait.

